frames.caption: A grand scene unfolds in an ornate architectural setting, where a cascade of gold coins flows from a high balcony into a large pile below. A crowd of people stands in awe, raising their hands towards the spectacle, illuminated by the golden glow of the coins.
frames.description: The scene is set in a majestic, temple-like structure with intricate carvings and domes, suggesting a historical or mythical context. The focus is on the dramatic waterfall of gold coins, which captivates the crowd gathered below.

frames.caption: A grand architectural hall is filled with a cascade of golden coins pouring from an ornate structure above. A crowd of people stands in awe, reaching towards the glistening treasure, creating a scene of wonder and excitement.
frames.description: The scene takes place in a majestic, ancient hall with intricate architectural details. A massive flow of gold coins descends from a central structure, forming a large pile on the ground. People are gathered around, captivated by the spectacle.
